{"title":"Durango Derby 2024 Registration is Open!","link":"https://theradavist.com/durango-derby-2024-registration-is-open/","date":1705335345000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-83.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Last year, we featured Reportage of the inaugural <a href=\"https://www.durangoderby.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Durango Derby</a>, a MTB race weekend in the (mtb) historic town of Durango. Today, the Derby announced <a href=\"https://www.bikereg.com/durangoderby\" target=\"_blank\">2024 registration is open</a>. Read more here.<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-165.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bikereg.com/durangoderby\" target=\"_blank\">Durango Derby opened registration</a> for the 2024 Durango Derby this morning at 9am MST. For those who made it out the event last year, the event is stoked ya’ll had a great time, and for those who were not able to make it, let’s change that for this year…</p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-290.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/DurangoDerby_23-211.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The Derby has got some exciting news to go along with announcing the registration opening; here are the bullet points:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>As part of the event’s mission to get more people on bikes, <strong><em>All Women, Non-Binary, and 18 and Under Categories are 25% discounted</em></strong>. No codes required.</li>\n<li>Durango Derby will be the series finals for the Singletracks Series in 2024</li>\n<li>Race day is <strong><em>Sunday, Sept. 1st 2024 – Labor Day Weekend</em></strong>.</li>\n<li>The event is adding a new “Downcountry Dominator” race within the race. Best of 4 timed DH segments within the XC stages.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See our Reportage here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2023-durango-derby-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\">Doing the 2023 Durango Derby</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/durango-derby-2024-registration-is-open/\">Durango Derby 2024 Registration is Open!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ca8a92979cdb1d840291d7e59d3e53580bac467b5eb9648bd19247e5b31e42b6","category":"Cycling"}